physical_appearance: This is a photograph of a view of Singapore from a high view point. The photograph features numerous roofed buildings, with an empty field in the center. The background of the photograph shows the coast, with a large number of ships at the harbour. The forefront of the photograph shows some treetops at the edge of a cliff, with a man sitting near the bottom-right. The title is written at the bottom, below the photograph.
title_text: Photograph album of views and portraits in the Punjab, Cashmere, Ceylon, Burma, Penang, Singapore, and Java Singapore
